info.name: TrimbleZebraPrinting
info.summary: Trimble Zebra Printing was built to simplify and standardize ZPL printing in the Trimble Facilities. This includes features, such as DPI scaling, to improve printing automation. Upscaling DPI results in a loss of quality. Matching DPIs or downscaling is recommended.
